Free phone wallpaper and a limited edition postcard set, so you can celebrate the Keen Project Safari Porsches! 🌄

Over the past two weeks, we’ve been creating art for the Keen Project Safari Porsche community - and now you can take home a piece of this celebration:

Download one of the free phone wallpapers to get some action to your lock screen.

And get 1 of only 17 limited edition postcard sets, portraying the Safari Porsches in action at the Appalachian Adventure trip.

Check out www.runoff.studio/keenproject (or the link in our bio) to download your free phone wallpaper and to get your own postcard set!

#safari911 #porscheoffroad #911safari #thekeenproject #safariporsche #offroadporsche #porsche911safari #appalachianadventure #keenproject #porscheoverland

Will it crank? During the @highsnobiety shoot one of the first things that happened was I got # 1 stuck in a deeper than I thought mud puddle. After pulling it out and letting it drain a bit we got it fired back up and filmed for the rest of the day! Goes to show the great engineering @porsche put into these cars when designed. The flat six runs even after being sunk! @yonischley

Throw back to 1999. “Testing” @mcgrathkeen’s factory GT2 racecar at the local airport. No I’m not wearing Jencos (I wish). The motor proved to be very strong and the car was the “right” purchase. Unfortunately it doesn’t still live in the collection but you can’t win them all. I will never forget sitting on the raw tub where the rear seat of a normal 911 would be holding onto the roll cage and seeing 6,000+ rpm in 6th gear on the tach. 🚗💨

The Bitburger🍺 Mild Seven🚬 1995 Supercup at @pecatl getting ready to be on display circa 2017. We are edging 25 years of ownership of this pup. The first racecar I ever drove 💚💙💛💚 @mcgrathkeen @ray.shaffer
@gvsskier using his Keen Project Safari to tow his snow bike to the trails 🙌 #TheKeenProject #SnowBike

@stoneisland_official + @danielarsham Project from about a year ago. There is just something about the desert! @bridgehampton_motoring_club behind the wheel of the Unimog. @elkineditions with the amazing 🎥 work. Safari 19 causing the trouble 😂 Apparently we weren’t supposed to do “donuts”. I’ve always argued big drifts aren’t “donuts”.
@mcgrathkeen back in the red 993 GT2 R game. Shout out to @porschecolorado We love it!
The Frog 🐸 is on display at the @pecatl heritage gallery for their current “Icons” exhibition. @zriggz with the awesome shots 📸👌 @porsche

Great day at @racethefirm RallyX. # 1 did amazing and then I drove it 5 hours home. There is nothing like a @porsche 911. The most versatile sports car on the planet! I highly recommend checking The Firm out if you have never been! 🎥 @chasinglaps  #TheKeenProject
📸 great shots from 1-2 @kmmediallc 3-4 @52nd_st_media  5-8 @eddiemikiphoto @racethefirm #TheKeenProject

28 years later……. Enjoyed the 993 RS at @ingramexperience VIR event. This is the 3rd different track it’s seen since my ownership and will continue to see more as originally intended by Porsche! Just wish Bob was riding with me. He would have loved it. It’s been a tough few days but was glad to be at a place that he loved and with people that loved him 🙌❤️ @virnow

Say hello to @mykcsupercar’s # 31. “Lighter Green” aka Jade Green with old VW interior material. This pup has all the option boxes checked ✅ Including short gear set and 3.4 built engine. #TheKeenProject
@smokiesgt3 Photo dump. As always. What a weekend! #SmokiesGT3

#TheKeenProject - Aspen to Alpine is a wrap. Lotsa miles, laughs, slides and incredible moments along the way! Special thanks to @zwart and @diegoriba for showing around their playgrounds. Participants were @allan_thom_  in # 2, @mikepollock & @9six4 in # 4, @ingramcollection in # 6, Dan in # 10, @mhsongjr in # 11, @kevinlmarshall & @runtahoe in # 13, @diegoriba & @jdhtwelve18 in # 14, @air_cld & @mollyplummercook in # 18, Groobz & @leyla_portela in # 23, @mykcsupercar in # 31 and @cavanok in # 33. Also thanks to @codyhunt155 & @fvatter for hostin and helpin! The cars and scenery were only topped by the amazing people in our group 🙌🍻❤️

CALLING ALL PORSCHES. RiverWerks /// Porsches At The Mill will be hosted at @habershammills Complex, just North of Atlanta, in Demorest, GA October 21st, 2023. @autohaussocial and @lehmank with #TheKeenProject are proud to announce @porsche / @pecatl as title sponsors along with the support of @hennessyporsche and @porscheatlantaperimeter. Come join us for a curated experience along the beautiful Soquee River where we will showcase some of Stuttgart's finest. Vehicle registration will open soon. No Porsche? No problem. Come enjoy cars, food, live music, and help us raise money for @songsforkids.

 More details to come. Hope to see you there!
Say hello to # 34. Ice Green Metallic over green leather/Pascha woven suede. Shout out to @winningauto with the amazing photos 🙌. Enjoy your Safari @hockeyguy626! #TheKeenProject

Photos I took at Rennsport 2 in April of 2004. Haven’t missed one since and don’t plan to anytime soon! By the photos you can see what I am into. GT1, big turbos and lifted 911. Not much has changed. The Last photo is of me on the banking learning how to drive.
Throwback to when Andrew Davis and Leh Keen took the Grand-Am season crown about twelve years ago. 🏆💥
